## Linking to Code

### Commit Messages
Format: `DT-XXX: Brief description`
```
git commit -m "DT-42: Fix password validation for special characters"
```

### PR Titles
Format: `DT-XXX: PR title`
```
gh pr create --title "DT-42: Fix login validation" --body "Fixes DT-42"
```

### PR Body Template
```markdown
## Summary
Fixes DT-XXX

## Changes
- Change 1
- Change 2

## Test Plan
